      <strong>About producing Other People's Business:</strong>
      <li>This comic updates three times a week: Monday, Wednesday, and Friday.</li>
      <li>In addition, you can go to the forums to get the cartoonist's commentary and chat about the comic, or if you have a livejournal, you can subscribe to the OPB community and get notices on the updates and the commentary.</li>
      <li>I'm not the best artist in the world, but I like practicing and playing with new techniques. I hope the art will be fairly consistent within each issue, but the styles may differ from issue to issue.</li>
      <li>The comic is divided into issues of anywhere from 20 â€“ 28 pages. Print editions will be available, and will collect five to six issues. They will be available for purchase in the OPB store.</li>
