  <p>
    <ul>
      <strong>About the story in Other People's Business:</strong>
      <li>What is the story about? After a tragic event, down-on-her-luck Daniela "Danny" Alvarez is being coaxed back into a life of normality by her best friend, sensible sous chef Mercedes, when a smart-mouthed sleazy little thief bursts through Danny's window and drags her into a world full of conspiracies, cults, and evil corporations, and accidentally gets Danny on the road to feeling human again.</li>
      <li>My attempt is to make a comic that is funny and interesting. However, if you are the sort of person who requires happy endings for everyone, this is not a comic you should be reading as it will not fulfill that requirement.</li>
      <li>The characters are lying to you.</li>
      <li>The beliefs of the characters are not meant to mirror my own beliefs, or the beliefs of anyone in particular; they are simply meant to make for an interesting fictional story.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>
